Hail, traveler of the Land of Hyperbola. You
stand before the Celestial Portal of Arctanh, a
gateway that bridges the known with the
unknown.
SF_Monster
To pass through, you must resonate with the
ebb and flow of arctanh. Tell me, can you
determine the derivative of artanh(x) at
x = 1/Sqrt[2].
SF_Monster
If you calculate the derivative of the
logarithm expresion of the arctanh(x), the
solution should become easy.
SF_Monster
Masterfully discerned, traveler! With your
understanding of the derivative of arctanh,
you've attuned to the portal's frequency.
Step forth, and journey into the realms beyond.

You have earned 100 PV and 100 PM.

traveler. The portal seeks resonance, a harmony
that can only be achieved with precise
understanding.
